'''雷迪夫網'''（{{lang-en|Rediff.com}}）是[[印度|印度]]結合[[新聞|新聞]]、資訊、娛樂、購物的[[入口網站|入口網站]]，成立於1996年<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.financialexpress.com/news/rediff.com-reports-q1-results-india-revenue-up-42/339965/ |title=Rediff.Com reports Q1 results: India revenue up 42%|publisher=The Financial Express|date=2008-07-02|accessdate=2020-11-12|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://rediffonthenet.com/about/index.html|title=About Rediff.com|website=RediffOnTheNet.com|accessdate=2020-11-12|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20000118122756/http://rediffonthenet.com/about/index.html|archivedate=2000-01-18}}</ref>，總部位於[[孟買|孟買]]，在[[班加羅爾|班加羅爾]]、[[新德里|新德里]]、[[紐約市|紐約市]]設有辦事處<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.businesswireindia.com/PressRelease.asp?b2mid=20976|title=Rediff Launches All New Blogs Platform in 9 Languages |publisher=Rediff.com India Ltd|via=Business Wire India|date=2009-12-01|accessdate=2020-11-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100113142032/http://www.businesswireindia.com/PressRelease.asp?b2mid=20976|archivedate=2010-01-13}}</ref>。截至2009年，雷迪夫網約有300名員工<ref name="employees"/>。

根據[[Alexa_Internet|Alexa Internet]]報導，雷迪夫網2020年的網路流量在印度排名第51位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.alexa.com/topsites/countries/IN|title=Top Sites in India|publisher=Alexa Internet|accessdate=2020-11-14|language=en}}</ref>，網站訪問者大多來自印度，其餘地區訪問者則以[[美國|美國]]、[[卡達|卡達]]為主<ref name="alexa">{{cite web|title=rediff.com Competitive Analysis, Marketing Mix and Traffic – Alexa|url=https://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/rediff.com|accessdate=2020-11-14|website=alexa.com|language=en}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
雷迪夫網的域名'''Rediff.com'''於1996年在印度註冊使用<ref name="IDR">{{cite web|title=India completes 20 years of commercial internet|url=http://www.indiadigitalreview.com/news/india-completes-15-years-of-commercial-internet|website=India Digital Review|accessdate=2020-11-14|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315105428/http://www.indiadigitalreview.com/news/india-completes-15-years-of-commercial-internet|archivedate=2014-03-15|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，網站創立初期提供[[電子郵件|電子郵件]]（Rediffmail）<ref>{{cite web|title=How Rediff On The NeT first created a template for the Hindu Right online in the 1990s|url=https://theprint.in/pageturner/excerpt/rediff-on-the-net-first-created-template-for-hindu-right-online-in-1990s/|website=ThePrint|date=2019-12-15|accessdate=2020-11-14|language=en}}</ref>、電子產品及周邊商品[[網路購物|網路購物]]服務。

2001年，雷迪夫網因為以[[美國存託憑證|美國存託憑證]]進行[[IPO|IPO]]時所提交的[[招股說明書|招股說明書]]存在重大漏洞而被指控違反《[[1933年證券法|1933年證券法]]》<ref>{{cite news|title=Cauley Geller Bowman & Coates, LLP Announces Class Action Lawsuit Against Rediff.com India Ltd. Seeking Damages on Behalf of Purchasers of Rediff American Depository Shares – REDF|url=http://globenewswire.com/news-release/2001/05/25/281272/17393/en/Cauley-Geller-Bowman-Coates-LLP-Announces-Class-Action-Lawsuit-Against-Rediff-com-India-Ltd-Seeking-Damages-on-Behalf-of-Purchasers-of-Rediff-American-Depository-Shares-REDF.html|website=GlobeNewswire|date=2001-05-25|accessdate=2020-11-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180624040030/http://globenewswire.com/news-release/2001/05/25/281272/17393/en/Cauley-Geller-Bowman-Coates-LLP-Announces-Class-Action-Lawsuit-Against-Rediff-com-India-Ltd-Seeking-Damages-on-Behalf-of-Purchasers-of-Rediff-American-Depository-Shares-REDF.html|archivedate=2018-06-24|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，此案最終在2009年以和解收場<ref>{{cite web|url=http://securities.stanford.edu/filings-case.html?id=101787|title=Case Summary Rediff.com India Ltd. Securities Litigation|publisher=Stanford Law School|accessdate=2020-11-15|language=en}}</ref>。

2001年4月，雷迪夫網收購以[[印度裔美國人|印度裔美國人]]為主要受眾的紐約報紙《{{link-en|印度海外|India Abroad}}》<ref name="ia">{{cite news|url=http://www.rediff.com/news/2008/apr/10mrraju.htm|title=Pioneering publisher Gopal Raju passes away|date=2008-04-01|publisher=India Abroad|accessdate=2020-11-15|language=en}}</ref>。2007年，雷迪夫網宣布多媒體影音分享平台上線<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.livemint.com/Industry/LmTno8d9USWKV5ddqJW2sM/Now-share-videos-music-on-Rediffs-iShare.html|title= Now share videos, music on Rediff’s iShare |last=Mehra|first=Priyanka |publisher=Mint|date=2007-07-01|accessdate=2020-11-15|language=en}}</ref>。2010年，雷迪夫網旗下電子郵件服務的行動平台Rediffmail NG正式啟用<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/2010/10/21/stories/2010102151751800.htm |title=Mobile email service from Rediff.com |publisher=[[印度報|印度報]]|date=2010-10-02|accessdate=2020-11-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101028223147/http://www.hindu.com/2010/10/21/stories/2010102151751800.htm|archivedate=2010-10-28|language=en}}</ref>。2012年，為旗下新聞服務啟用專為[[Android|Android]]平台開發的[[APP|APP]]<ref>{{cite news|title=REDIFF NEWS APP FOR ANDROID OS LAUNCHED|url=https://www.firstpost.com/tech/news-analysis/rediff-news-app-for-android-os-launched-3608531.html|publisher=[[第一郵報|第一郵報]]|date=2012-12-18|accessdate=2020-11-15|language=en}}</ref>。

2016年4月，雷迪夫網鑒於當時自身財務狀況難以向[[美國證券交易委員會|美國證券交易委員會]]提交定期報告以及滿足其他監管要求，決定從[[那斯達克|那斯達克]]下市<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/rediffcom-informs-nasdaq-of-intent-to-withdraw-american-depository-shares-from-listing-and-registration-300258335.html|title=Rediff.com Informs Nasdaq Of Intent To Withdraw American Depository Shares From Listing And Registration|publisher=Rediff India Limited|agency=[[美通社|美通社]]|date=2016-04-27|accessdate=2020-11-15|language=en}}</ref>。

